<p>The <code>restart</code> tag restarts page processing.</p>

<h2>Syntax</h2>
<pre>{open}restart{close}</pre>

<h2>Use Case</h2>
<pre>{open}action 'process'{close}
  {open}!-- Process data --{close}
  {open}set $message = 'Done!'{close}
  {open}restart{close}  {open}!-- Restart to show message --{close}
{open}/action{close}

{open}if $message{close}
  {open}$message{close}
{open}/if{close}</pre>

<h2>Note</h2>
<p>Restart re-executes the page from the beginning with current state.</p>
<p>Useful after form processing to show updated data.</p>
